## Clinical Neurobiology

Below you will find links to brief summaries of the diseases mentioned in the course or discussed in the forums.  These are meant to provide only a brief introduction for those who are interested, and more information can be found in the links included in the descriptions.  This list is by no means complete, and will continue to grow and evolve as the course progresses.

